				<td colspan="2"><span>Bards are one of the classes in which no race really sticks out.
<br />

<br />
Humans could easily be called the worst, due to lack of vision and nothing else (Forget culturals, things like that get more and more useless as expansions get added) but realisticly since they changed vision its not nearly as bad as it was back in the day, and bards get songs for that if things get bad in an emergency or something.
