				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Best Bard Race<a name="71004"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Dec 14 04 10:31 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I did notice a few things when I started a Vah Shir Bard on a new server, just for a change of pace.
<br />

<br />
1: Couldn't do the newbie drum quest in Kelethin due to insufficient faction. Therefore, Kitty bards start with lower Old world Bard faction.
<br />

<br />
2: Noticed that prices at vendors were higher in Vah Shir than elsewhere. (and yes, I'm taking into account faction AND charisma)
<br />

<br />
3: Don't Vah Shir get a large size experience points penalty?
<br />

<br />
4: Kitty's can only be agnostic. (not a big deal)
<br />

<br />
5: There was one more thing, I can't remember at the moment, will modify post shortly when I think of it. </span></td>
